id: pmc-qjl9
title: Production release readiness pass for pm-changelog 2026.5.23-5
description: "Full continuation pass requested on 2026-05-23 to make pm-changelog production and release ready after unreleased repository commits. Scope covers GitHub issues and CI state through gh, dependency/vulnerability checks, strict pm governance, extension version alignment, clean temporary pm install testing, self-generated changelog output, npm publication, GitHub release creation, and final commit/push state."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[5]: github,governance,npm,release,verification
created_at: "2026-05-23T21:39:36.740Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-23T21:42:48.261Z"
deadline: "2026-05-23T00:00:00.000Z"
author: codex-pm-changelog
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: "- GitHub issues, PRs, Actions, releases, vulnerability alerts, and free-feature repository settings are verified with gh.\\n- npm outdated and npm audit report no actionable dependency or vulnerability findings.\\n- pm validate strict checks pass after governance updates.\\n- npm run release:check passes from the repository checkout.\\n- A clean temporary folder can install the package with pm install from npm or local package source and run pm changelog generate.\\n- CHANGELOG.md is regenerated by pm-changelog itself and changelog:check passes.\\n- package version 2026.5.23-5 is committed, pushed, published to npm, tagged, and released publicly on GitHub if all gates pass."
reviewer: steve
risk: medium
confidence: high
sprint: 2026-05-release
release: v2026.05.23-5
resolution: "Completed current production-readiness pass for pm-changelog 2026.5.23-5: dependency locks updated, extension runtime version aligned, free Dependabot version-update config added, GitHub issue/CI/security report state verified with gh, npm dependency/audit checks clean, strict pm validation clean, release gate passing, and clean temp local pm install smoke passing."
expected_result: "pm-changelog 2026.5.23-5 is release-ready, governed by strict pm records, installable through pm package flows, self-generates its changelog, and can be published to npm/GitHub after final changelog regeneration."
actual_result: "gh checks found all issues closed, no PRs, latest CI success, empty Dependabot alerts, enabled vulnerability alerts and automated security fixes, and public/free-feature repo settings. npm outdated returned {}, npm audit reported 0 vulnerabilities, npm run release:check passed with 18 tests and pack dry-run, strict pm validate passed, and /tmp/pm-changelog-2026-5-23-5-local-ulnPKD verified pm install plus changelog generation."
