comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-23T21:39:36.740Z",codex-pm-changelog,Started from a clean main branch at origin/main; package.json is ahead of the latest published npm dist-tag and needs a current release pass.
  "2026-05-23T21:42:31.008Z",codex,"GitHub evidence: gh issue list shows issues #1, #2, and #3 all closed; gh pr list is empty; gh run list shows latest CI run 26343824903 completed successfully; gh repo view reports PUBLIC visibility, main default branch, Issues enabled, Projects/Wiki disabled, MIT license, README homepage, and release topics. Dependabot alerts endpoint returned [], vulnerability alerts endpoint returned HTTP 204 enabled, and automated-security-fixes reports enabled=true paused=false. Code scanning endpoint reports no analysis found and secret scanning endpoint reports disabled; no paid GitHub security feature was enabled."
  "2026-05-23T21:42:32.863Z",codex,"Dependency evidence: npm update refreshed @types/node lockfile entry to 25.9.1 and @unbrained/pm-cli lockfile entry to 2026.5.18. npm outdated --json returned {}; npm audit --omit=dev --json and npm audit in release:check reported 0 vulnerabilities."
  "2026-05-23T21:42:34.235Z",codex,"Verification evidence: npm run release:check passed for pm-changelog@2026.5.23-5 with tsc --noEmit, 18 node:test tests, npm audit --omit=dev, npm pack --dry-run with 25 files, and changelog:check reporting CHANGELOG.md up to date."
  "2026-05-23T21:42:36.227Z",codex,"Temp install evidence: clean project /tmp/pm-changelog-2026-5-23-5-local-ulnPKD ran pm init, pm install local checkout --project, created and closed a smoke Task, ran pm changelog generate, produced CHANGELOG.md containing Verify local 2026.5.23-5 install, and pm package doctor --project --json --strict-exit returned ok=true with zero warnings."
